.TH FEDORA-L10N 1 "2026-02-15" "Daniel Nylander" "Fedora L10n Manual"
.SH NAME
fedora-l10n - View Fedora translation progress via Weblate
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B fedora-l10n
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBfedora-l10n\fR is a GTK4/Adwaita application that shows translation progress of Fedora projects via the Weblate API. It lists all 127 Fedora translation projects with per-language statistics, color-coded progress bars, component-level drill-down, search and filter, direct Weblate links, and local caching with rate limiting.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.SH KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS
.TP
.B Ctrl+Q
Quit the application
.TP
.B F5
Refresh the current data
.TP
.B Ctrl+/
Show keyboard shortcuts dialog
.TP
.B Ctrl+E
Export current view to CSV or JSON format
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/fedora-l10n/
Configuration files.
.TP
.I ~/.cache/fedora-l10n/
Cached data.
